    inputsNeeded: "",
    content: "## The 8-Point Pre-Roll Call\n\nProducer calls each one. Person responsible confirms out loud.\n\n- [ ] \"Camera A — rolling?\" _(\"Rolling.\")_\n- [ ] \"Camera B — rolling?\" _(\"Rolling.\")_\n- [ ] \"Sound?\" _(\"Speed.\")_\n- [ ] \"Lavs hot?\" _(\"Hot, levels good.\")_\n- [ ] \"Boom in?\" _(\"In frame.\")_\n- [ ] \"Slate?\" _(Visible slate, clap.)_\n- [ ] \"Talent ready?\" _(\"Ready.\")_\n- [ ] \"And… action.\"\n\n## The Post-Take Check\n\n- [ ] Producer says \"cut\" — not the DP, not the talent\n- [ ] Audio op confirms no peaks or dropouts\n- [ ] DP confirms focus held\n- [ ] Producer marks circle-take or NG in notes\n- [ ] Reset takes <30 seconds for the next take",
