    loops: ["Content Loop"],
    purpose: "The Palmer House palette. Click any swatch to copy the hex.",
    ownerRole: "company",
    whenToUse: "**USAGE RULES** — Spotlight is for one element per screen — the one thing we want clicked. Curtain is for drama (the Pals, second-tier emphasis). Sage Reel is the quiet adult in the room — use sparingly, it ages well.",
    trigger: "",
    inputsNeeded: "",
    content: "### Core Palette\n\n- **Stage Black** — `#1F1A17` _(Primary · Backgrounds)_\n- **Spotlight** — `#F26522` _(Accent · CTAs)_\n- **Curtain** — `#5C2A82` _(Secondary · Drama)_\n- **Paper** — `#F6F1E8` _(Neutral · Surfaces)_\n\n### Support Palette\n\n- **Studio Ink** — `#2A2320` _(Surface dark)_\n- **Spotlight HI** — `#FF7A3A` _(Hover)_\n- **Curtain HI** — `#7A3FA8` _(Hover)_\n- **Sage Reel** — `#8FA892` _(Quiet accent)_\n- **Cream** — `#FBF8F2` _(Page base)_\n- **Success** — `#3E7D57` _(Affirmations)_\n- **Danger** — `#C24B3B` _(Warnings)_\n- **Muted** — `#7A7267` _(Captions)_\n\n> **USAGE RULES** — Spotlight is for one element per screen — the one thing we want clicked. Curtain is for drama (the Pals, second-tier emphasis). Sage Reel is the quiet adult in the room — use sparingly, it ages well.",
